{"tid":1990919,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【Let it Frozen】iOS 13.4.1大bug 收通知會hang機！","createTime":"2020-04-27T05:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T06:51:58.000Z","uid":232237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"367dcd3391da7190a53bfd5435fe00399d6351dc","tid":1990919,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T05:25:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://wepro180.com/tech-news/%E3%80%90let-it-frozen%E3%80%91ios-13-4-1%E5%A4%A7bug-%E6%94%B6%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9C%83hang%E6%A9%9F%EF%BC%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwepro180.com%2Ftech-news%2F%25E3%2580%2590let-it-frozen%25E3%2580%2591ios-13-4-1%25E5%25A4%25A7bug-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%259C%2583hang%25E6%25A9%259F%25EF%25BC%2581%2F&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4LXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=66e891de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wepro180.com/tech-news/%E3%80%90let-it-frozen%E3%80%91ios-13-4-1%E5%A4%A7bug-%E6%94%B6%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9C%83hang%E6%A9%9F%EF%BC%81/</a><br />\n<br />\niPhone 同 iPad 用家，大家升咗 iOS 13.4.1 未呀，升咗嗱？恭喜晒！因為你同小編都係受害者，會受到呢個 bug 影響，嗱嗱臨去閂咗 notifications 佢先啦！iPhone SE2機主都係呀！<br />\n<br />\n上星期 Apple 為 iOS 推出新版本後，好快就有人喺 Twitter 上表示伏已中，因為更新作業系統後，只要 iOS 裝置收到一個內有意大利國旗 emoji加巴基斯坦辛德語（Sindhi）嘅通知（notifications)，成部裝置就會求 touch 不得、求閂不能，hang 機 hang 到完全用唔到。其後再被證實原來唔需要意大利國旗，單係 Sindhi 文字已經有相同效果。暫時被證實會出事嘅 app 通知包括 WhatsApp、Messages、Twitter 等等，但理論上應該係任何 app 都得，而且最重要係有人 send 俾你就死，唔需要你打開嚟睇。<br />\n<br />\n由於呢個bug係跟喺最新嘅 iOS 版本上，所以現階段 Apple 應該唔會咁快有新版本推出修補漏洞，大家要自救，就麻煩入去設定，將接收所有 notifications 嘅設定關閉，方法係 Settings&gt;Notifications&gt;Screen Time，取消 Allow Notifications 就得。當然大家從前就再收唔到任何新通知，下下都要自己入去睇，但如果你唔嫌麻煩其實可以唔使識，因為你只要強制 reboot 過部機之後，依然係可以用得返嘅！<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"https://zd.net/2xeRfwM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzd.net%2F2xeRfwM&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4LXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=83ff611f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zd.net/2xeRfwM</a>"},{"pid":"3daa9387f868525cd9ebc52b4eda86a85024558c","tid":1990919,"uid":232237,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T05:25:15.000Z","msg":"用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6aa266e7c85b9325fdb27cda6d767be133ba3f","tid":1990919,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T05:27:58.000Z","msg":"只要 iOS 裝置收到一個內有意大利國旗 emoji加巴基斯坦辛德語（Sindhi）嘅通知（notifications)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊個先會收到呢啲通知"},{"pid":"51a122636e9714c3257ba8a1e7325ee9204d2345","tid":1990919,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a6aa266e7c85b9325fdb27cda6d767be133ba3f","tid":1990919,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T05:27:58.000Z","msg":"只要 iOS 裝置收到一個內有意大利國旗 emoji加巴基斯坦辛德語（Sindhi）嘅通知（notifications)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊個先會收到呢啲通知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"特登整估你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7056bea030c1df17bffd5f674c1476badf9afa00","tid":1990919,"uid":59920,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T06:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用家問題"},{"pid":"718b843da2d30f4a2b17a642c3e85012929b10ab","tid":1990919,"uid":28446,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"叫人熄晒所有notification<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如叫人熄埋部iphone直到個bug fix左 咁就一定唔會中bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98b91e161171b4a46c9fbda59881a5b494808ae","tid":1990919,"uid":158645,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T07:00:13.000Z","msg":"毒撚先用notification<br />\n熄咗佢就可以"},{"pid":"c2f32e2d0af35aabe192658612729e89d9649705","tid":1990919,"uid":266697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,